.TH "pending_reboot_show" 9 "pending_reboot_show" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
pending_reboot_show \- sysfs implementaton for read pending_reboot
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "ssize_t" pending_reboot_show
.BI "(struct kobject *kobj "  ","
.BI "struct kobj_attribute *attr "  ","
.BI "char *buf "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "kobj" 12
Kernel object for this attribute
.IP "attr" 12
Kernel object attribute
.IP "buf" 12
The buffer to display to userspace
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Stores default value as 0
When current_value is changed this attribute is set to 1 to notify reboot may be required
